<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>404 - Territorio Inexplorado</title>

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=MedievalSharp&family=Cinzel:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">

    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #2b1d0e;
            background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #2b1d0e 0, #2b1d0e 1px, #1f140a 0, #1f140a 50%);
            font-family: 'MedievalSharp', cursive;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0;
            overflow: hidden; /* Para que no haya scroll */
        }

        .parchment {
            background-color: #f4e4bc;
            background-image: url("https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/aged-paper.png");
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #d7c496;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Efecto de quemadura en el borde (opcional, decorativo) */
        .parchment::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 40px rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.5);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .error-code {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-size: 8rem;
            color: #8f260a; /* Rojo sangre seca */
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        h2 {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            color: #2c1e16;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #5d4037;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .dragon-icon {
            font-size: 5rem;
            color: #5d4037;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            opacity: 0.8;
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
            100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
        }

        .btn-return {
            background-color: #2c1e16;
            color: #d4af37;
            border: 2px solid #d4af37;
            padding: 10px 30px;
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .btn-return:hover {
            background-color: #d4af37;
            color: #2c1e16;
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.4);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="parchment">
        <i class="bi bi-question-circle dragon-icon"></i>

        <div class="error-code">404</div>

        <h2>¡Aquí hay dragones!</h2>

        <p>
            Parece que te has aventurado demasiado lejos en la niebla.<br>
            El pergamino que buscas ha sido reducido a cenizas o nunca existió en nuestros mapas.
        </p>

        <a href="/" class="btn-return">
            <i class="bi bi-compass"></i> Volver a la Aldea
        </a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>